location.fullValue: Danville Plan, Nino Homes at Arboleda

data.description: This 2 Bed, 1.5 Bath house is a hidden gem in King City, with just enough charm to win you over! You’ll love the crown molding throughout that adds a touch of elegance. With 1,009 sq ft, you can cozy up next to the fire for the holidays, relax on your patio furniture or enjoy the warm fall evenings as you tend to your garden. This beautiful home has been renovated with various amenities totaling over $40K! Improvements include: interior/exterior paint, reinforced fence, energy efficient shatter resistant noise reduction windows, faux wood blinds throughout, blackout shades in garage, new insulated garage door & opener, new front door, new screen door & awning, luxury vinyl plank flooring on the ground floor, new vanities, vessel sinks, faucets, lighting and quartz countertops throughout, new stainless steel appliances and various fixtures/hardware. The second level with two carpeted bedrooms were replaced in 2021. Washer and dryer convey. Pre-qualified buyers only.
